ement-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-37a2fa1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"37a2fa1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"980\" height=\"944\" src=\"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-04-at-23.47.58-1024x986.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-12416\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-04-at-23.47.58-1024x986.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-04-at-23.47.58-300x289.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-04-at-23.47.58-768x740.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-04-at-23.47.58-467x450.jpeg 467w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-04-at-23.47.58.jpeg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 980px) 100vw, 980px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3311575 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"3311575\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cc6b9eb e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"cc6b9eb\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-93f7e4a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"93f7e4a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Itinerary<\/h3>\n<p><b>Early Morning Pick-Up:<br><\/b>Your journey begins before sunrise, as our driver picks you up from your riad or hotel in Marrakech. You&#8217;ll be driven to the launch site, where you&#8217;ll enjoy a warm welcome with tea or coffee as the balloon is prepared for flight.<\/p>\n<p><b>Hot Air Balloon Ride:<br><\/b>Take off into the sky and marvel at the stunning sunrise over the Marrakech region. The peaceful flight provides panoramic views of the majestic Atlas Mountains, lush valleys, and desert plains, offering a unique perspective of Morocco\u2019s natural beauty.<\/p>\n<p><b>Berber Breakfast:<br><\/b>After landing, you&#8217;ll be treated to a delicious traditional Berber breakfast in a local tent or home. Enjoy freshly baked bread, honey, olives, and mint tea while immersing yourself in authentic Moroccan hospitality.<\/p>\n<p><b>Return to Marrakech:<br><\/b>Our driver will take you back to your accommodation in Marrakech, arriving by mid-morning, leaving you the rest of the day to explore the city at your leisure.<\/p>\n<p><b>Highlights:<\/b><\/p>\n<p>Witness a stunning sunrise over Marrakech and the Atlas Mountains.<\/p>\n<p>Enjoy a peaceful hot air balloon flight with incredible views.<\/p>\n<p>Savor a traditional Berber breakfast after landing.<\/p>\n<p>Relax with round-trip transportation from your accommodation.<\/p>\n<p>This hot air balloon experience is perfect for adventurers, couples, and families looking to add a magical touch to their Marrakech trip. Don&#8217;t miss the chance to soar above one of Morocco\u2019s most beautiful landscapes!<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Hot Air Balloon Adventure in Marrakech Experience the magic of Marrakech from the sky with our unforgettable hot air balloon ride! This one-of-a-kind adventure offers breathtaking views of the Atlas Mountains, desert landscapes, and traditional Berber villages, creating memories that will last a lifetime. Itinerary Early Morning Pick-Up:Your journey begins before sunrise, as our driver [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":0,"parent":11313,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-11684","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11684","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/5"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=11684"}],"version-history":[{"count":22,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11684\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":12785,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11684\/revisions\/12785"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11313"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=11684"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}